p.k: Robopat Today is the big Robot Battle day! Lola’s robot which looks like Pat has to face down Victor’s. But the boy cheats and breaks RoboPat. However Pat decides to sneak inside the broken robot shell and takes control of the machine to fight for his best fr...
p.d: Despite his small size and playful attitude, Pat is the hero that flies to his friends' rescue while avoiding numerous obstacles that get in his way.
